{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9321b982d9","title":"有关匈牙利事件的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af5e395459","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"9321b982d9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"32a47b4fc1","name":"何占枢"},{"id":"47f92c2cff","name":"陈堃"},{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"},{"id":"815cf794aa","name":"顾耀祖"},{"id":"861c5aba35","name":"联钦察"},{"id":"9aaf41f5ef","name":"邓明弢"},{"id":"b5d8d3d662","name":"周懋政"},{"id":"c2e6cf83f3","name":"曾铁超"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"19d2940d70","type":"title","text":"有关匈牙利事件的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"cc569eb4d5","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院曾铁超邓明弢顾耀祖陈堃联钦察何占枢周懋政","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"35839d55a9","type":"subtitle","text":"教师：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"ea18e0b615","type":"paragraph","text":"“匈牙利事件完全是匈牙利政府官僚主义，不了解群众生活所造成，不是反革命和帝国主义勾结所造成。”(曾铁超)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"d8611ce983","type":"paragraph","text":"“事物必先腐而后虫生，匈牙利反革命暴动是因为党搞肃反的后果，匈牙利党犯错误是匈牙利事件的主要原因。”“铁托敢于公开批评共产党是大胆的表现。”(邓明弢)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"c7fa956e09","type":"paragraph","text":"匈牙利事件后说：“马尔萨斯人口论有道理”(意指匈牙利事件是由粮食问题引起的)。(顾耀祖)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"11737e9795","type":"paragraph","text":"“党的和平外交政策是一种手段，因为我们的力量还不够强。”(陈堃)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"30de8f599d","type":"subtitle","text":"学生：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"6c2c98ea7d","type":"paragraph","text":"“匈牙利事件主要由于政府工作中的缺点所造成，苏联出兵匈牙利与蒋介石请美国人来中国是一样的。”(联钦察)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"9bd72eb9a9","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联出兵匈牙利是干涉，而不是援助，因为打着苏联的旗帜驻扎在别国的领土上。”(何占枢)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"db2f3fd40b","type":"paragraph","text":"“匈牙利事件，苏联第一次出兵是必要的，第二次出兵是错误。”(周懋政)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"},{"id":"3d1aeaddda","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选集》（中共成都工学院委员会办公室，1957年）。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9"}],"page":{"id":"648f84e9c2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9321b982d9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}